org.deeplearning4j.spark.time

Class TimeSourceProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.spark.time.TimeSourceProvider

  • public class TimeSourceProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    TimeSourceProvider: used to get a TimeSource via a static method.
    Defaults to the Network Time Protocol implementation NTPTimeSource, but can be switched to other implementations via the TIMESOURCE_CLASSNAME_PROPERTY system property.
